Tours Page:
  - Various tour packages categorized by destination or theme
  - Detailed information about each tour package, including itinerary, duration, and price
  - Booking option for each tour package
  - Reviews and testimonials from previous travellers

 The tour page will offer range of tours in a list.
 Within the tour page there will be the option to filter based on a variety of categories.
 These categories will destination, price, theme length and other accessibility options.

Each tour option will have an area in which users who have purchased the tour can offer feedback and reviews
This allows the user to see testimonials about the +/- of each tour.
